{"tid":2059230,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【國際戰線】有位Twitter手足專門通緝偽日本人5毛","createTime":"2020-06-10T18:22:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-13T17:42:27.000Z","uid":278414,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"dfe7cd7fa245cf5805b77f73623ad4f900b9089f","tid":2059230,"uid":278414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:22:59.000Z","msg":"轉貼<br />\n<br />\n(5毛個案①)絕對重犯 高級5毛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1270362588124033029?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1270362588124033029%3Fs%3D21&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=983b124b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1270362588124033029%3Fs%3D21&h=862a6536\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1270362588124033029?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PXKhDtj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPXKhDtj.jpg&h=f1ef76aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0WyBT1F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0WyBT1F.jpg&h=db11e3c7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RKkTWe0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRKkTWe0.jpg&h=90c9f9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n好多日本人辛苦幫手起Twitter做文宣，依條仆街5毛就去洗鳩人版，抹黑香港抗爭，分化。<br />\n有香港手足話鳩佢，佢就吊番香港人先係5毛黨，反抹黑。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nE條5毛亦曾經起手足既「香港抗議應援情報館」洗版，而且佢背景好有可能係Anifa，同中共有關係。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(5毛個案②)中級5毛<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1270638844015071233?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1270638844015071233%3Fs%3D21&d=zXAIbGZ2Qohx5%2Bb7%2FAbjRAQPoALeJAOsJ3HVvkpnkS8%3D&h=4a69a1e7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2F64uz0d5cd8jhu4e%2Fstatus%2F1270638844015071233%3Fs%3D21&h=c44cb64b\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/64uz0d5cd8jhu4e/status/1270638844015071233?s=21</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Y55wHOv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FY55wHOv.jpg&h=7b5fcbc8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nE條5毛抹黑香港抗爭，話抗爭係因為維尼和小江鬥爭而引起。<br />\n小江起香港洗黑錢，話維尼是為了阻止小江的惡行令小江轉唔到錢走，所以小江就起背後挑起香港人上街抗議，周庭就係小江手下。<br />\n詳細請自己入去睇，完全痴q線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最慘好多無知日本人信佢鳩up 中晒分化。<br />\n幫維尼洗白都算，仲要屈鳩周庭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望各位入去幫下手，支援一下日本國際戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗一定識日文，用中英日文宣圖或片都可以好有效果。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6770ccc861224c0ec354fdc0447485c7a16582d7","tid":2059230,"uid":171119,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:24:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bff051a9455c9f2fe5ef138df939091eb547cdd","tid":2059230,"uid":246588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:25:11.000Z","msg":"pushpushpushpushpush"},{"pid":"5036a9c68b558f4c818b2c8b2c5cbc90b2b692a4","tid":2059230,"uid":251732,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-10T18:27:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">死共狗無分種族，滅共剿匪人人有責<br />\n<br />\n香港需要山口二矢哩種英雄</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https: